latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.

I have to share many things about this two looks of mine❤️Many peoples have struggled and put their efforts too.This two looks were decided by me and sajan for my sister in law’s wedding but eventually it dint work out😕 and so this looks we decided to do in @shivbeldarepatil7380 wedding 🤩I feel so special because I was able to handle each and every thing in this looks cause before doing this look i was bit nervous about earrings and nose ring but it made the look best😍As it was a Manikarnika look i Wanted to try my best to carry it like @kanganaranaut she has spirit and that silent attitude which I don’t have😜While taking shots or pics and by seeing her pictures i have tried my best  in my shoot🥰 Best clicked and shooted by @rahul_wedding_films 
My second look which is northindian we thought of this look because i have not tried something out off the box And something different for @rohinikakade to do for me💋
The lehenga which Im wearing  it’s my wedding lehenga by @jayantireddylabel i recreated it by wearing @sajanandsaloni blouse and dupatta💗
About saree it’s @houseofneetalulla signature saree .when I called them first and i said i want this saree in black colour they were surprised 🤩
It takes one and a half month to complete this kind of saree but she have given me in 15 to 20 days .Special thanks to her assistant @shilpa.urg ❤️she is so polite and cooperative that we got the saree at our desired time .
@dyutibansalstudio who have customised clutch and footwear for me❤️l loved it so much and it suits on any outfit too❤️
And last about my jewellery it’s the best part by @raabtabyrahul they designed jewellery specially for this look. And @sameep_ved thank u for being so perfect and particulate about all small things as well when it comes for me 🥰
Specially toes accessories which is designed for me (in that one is sajan and one is me)🥰

Thank you everyone ❤️ & specially to my special one @saajanlipane thank you because of you it happened 🧿❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: The story of sajanandsaloni in caption 😉
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
इस दुनिया के शोर में तुमसा कोई मिल जाता है 
कुछ बातें हो या ना हो दिल ज़रूर बेहल जाता है।•
•
•
Wait is over here is full wedding highlights. 
Guys I get lot of Dm about my and sajan’s marriage. 
Here I go, we met in December 21st 2018 at the very first time. Before meeting I was sure I’ll reject this proposal and I was sure he will also because of age difference and big issue is we stay in hardly 1-2 km distance(almost same area). And we are in relatives also, my native place is same. So I’m dam sure I will not say yes at any cost.
So meeting start 11.30 at CCD, after three and half hours of  conversation we both sure age is just number and area doesn’t matters at all.
The Epic scene is, My aunt was his classmate and good friend too. So guys you can imagine what was pressure and what to do in this case.
But,
So at the end we both say Yes. And then both family will meet in January and the basic कादें-पोहे program  begins. 
Finally we got engaged on 5th of February 2019 and got married on 19th of April2019. 
Yes, it’s pure arrange marriage. 
He is a perfect guy for me an intelligent boy of family and the most wanted मुंडा😜❤️
So it’s our journey. Smooth and superb. 
Love you my own Honey❤️
•
•
@saajanlipane
